org.sql: SELECT members.user_id, role_id, members.project_id FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id INNER JOIN member_roles ON member_roles.member_id = members.id WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (members.user_id IS NULL OR projects.is_public = True AND members.user_id = 12)
